- • Note to Self:
- Develop healing potion vaporizer.
- Advantages:
- • Administer healing without touching dying person's mouth;
- • Have healing administered without others touching my mouth;
- • Undeath test;
- • Rejuvenating steam room for healing and relaxation after combat;
- • Potential new source of revenue;
- • Unconventional delivery method conceals healing from enemies;
- • Neutralize violent remains animated after deadbomb detonation.

